# 🚀 Multi-Agent AI Travel Planner

## 📌 Overview

An intelligent travel planning system that leverages **multiple AI agents** to collaboratively generate personalized travel itineraries based on user preferences.

The system simulates real-world planning by delegating tasks (such as destination research, itinerary generation, and recommendations) to specialized agents working together.

